						               													<description>Welcome to the Hexa Sea, General. This land is vital to our Nation. We must hold it at any cost, and remove the enemy's presence. Set a hold in the land of the Hexa Sea, bring forth our Army, and strike deep at the enemy headquarters. Win for us.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Hexa Sea is an abstract, terrain control wargame played on a modular map that changes every new game. You set hold on the map with your Headquarters, build new units and fight your opponent off the map.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The board is comprised of sea tiles and land pieces called Hexas. These Hexas are arranged over the board forming islands with land tiles. Controlling different numbers of Hexas allow the player to build different units, that interact between themselves in different ways. The goal of the game is to capture the Soldier controlling your opponent's Headquarters.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;3rd Best Overall Game, 3rd Best Art/Graphic Design, 2nd Best New Mechanic and 2nd Best Wargame at the 2013 Two-Player PnP Game Design Contest&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
